Z","msg":"爆就一定架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 幾時爆？天曉得，可能你買左之後即刻爆 (goto point 3) 又可能係幾年後先爆，但到時你現價買，都升多幾成了，到時先爆你都有好大既 buffer (又係 goto point 3)<br />\n<br />\n2. 爆既程度有幾多？跌 20% 好未 - 好多恨樓恨到發瘋既都會出來搶貨喇 (like 2008 年尾)<br />\n<br />\n3. 爆之時，會影響你幾多？計掂數加幾厘息都供到既，爆又關你乜事"},{"pid":"943b2239b2d1a63955083aac848c678c13b10958","tid":530363,"uid":42194,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"又係時候重溫林太金句<br />\n<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/013454_7904a5d8aa943c65bb9e0ab4039959ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F013454_7904a5d8aa943c65bb9e0ab4039959ff.jpg&h=b533f746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林太講左D 咩, 自己參透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4019b06fe4bd5e8a0c7626a9b20a0a28a2e2fc0a","tid":530363,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"中左居屋驚乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297ff82ae6db338384ce59fcabeb3241eb6f0161","tid":530363,"uid":12241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"又話爆 聽左十幾年啦 爆未？"},{"pid":"869d29b302347aa33d16ddbecc16b60c82d7fe2e","tid":530363,"uid":68556,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"爆左就即補地價  perfect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46421325ef264b9041cd9399e72ac4730e9c2e1","tid":530363,"uid":74241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:43:12.000Z","msg":"自己覺得會爆咪睇定啲先囉"},{"pid":"4c3d9a6751a64e90141cd9290a175b2a96fa1eff","tid":530363,"uid":105906,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":